The paper deals with understanding text in images, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed model is based on a transformer architecture, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model also involves iterative answer decoding, which is a technique commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
